Comment: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:38.60,Note,,0,0,0,,{these are all history books, but there's no way nor point to typeset all of them, and a note here would also look silly so alas}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.81,Top,,0,0,0,,This is the season of the fresh scent of young leaves.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.40,0:00:37.81,Top,,0,0,0,,The time when everything\Nsprouts so as to start new life.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.55,0:00:45.90,Top,,0,0,0,,Now, let me whisper gently \Nto your sleeping sensitivity.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe in deeply this sweet air.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.44,0:00:58.81,Top,,0,0,0,,I continue to talk today \Nto all of you living in the 21st century.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.10,0:01:06.47,Top,,0,0,0,,This is Ohara Noriko,\Nand my show {\i1}The 21st Century.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes! What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.33,0:01:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.46,0:01:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you see?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on a sec,\Nthey're just getting to the good part.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let me see too!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.49,0:01:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but the shock will be too much \Nfor a virgin like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.62,0:01:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.90,0:01:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that apartment building facing us?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.31,0:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.83,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one right in the middle.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, what's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.62,0:01:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.77,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the guys who are kind of cool\Nare all like that on the inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That would kill even a love of a hundred years.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy! {/I pity him}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yea... huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.98,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing that because he doesn't have a girlfriend.\NHe must be lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.74,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! That guy is just a massive horndog, \Nlike his entire body is made of dick tissue! {/cavernous body}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It just isn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew... that was refreshing!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.15,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.95,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you need a maiden? {shojo = young girl - probably with implication "virgin"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks. I'm good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wha... Wh-What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... need a maiden?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A maiden?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.81,0:04:07.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Yuno was no longer a maiden,\Nand I've also graduated from virginity. {solitary pleasures}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.09,0:04:14.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't know what attracted her to me, \Nbut I'm in love with her anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,There aren't many girls as cute as she is.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,And then, there's also that behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Above all, she's the daughter of a tycoon...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,She might just be too good for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.43,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good morning, Rokuro-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there. \NWhat are you making?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My special stamina meal!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.24,0:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is broiled eel, that's garlic steak, this is fermented soybeans, okra and grated yams.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.17,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's garlic chives{ osumashi??? clear soup?} and turtle soup​.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, a stamina drink...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can see right through you. {?????????? was "talk about one-track mind" - nc what's this conta that's in full view, maybe it's something about the bottle, maybe it's about the food, implying that all the dishes share some common theme that's somehow sex-related?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why isn't there a bathtub\Nat your place, Rokuro-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't because there isn't!{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is a bathhouse?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the other side!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously! {mou}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.92,0:05:44.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,I didn't think she had so little common sense.\NBut what the hell, she's cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.\NWhat do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.31,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Have I done something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.78,Top,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop making a mess, didn't I?! {??????????????????????????? the old subs had "stop putting the soap in the bath" but I'm certain they made it up, because I can't hear shit either; "fuun" can be poop so maybe she shat herself? chotto anta **** mou itsudai kara itte deshou!}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.70,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Get out! We're not gonna put up with that! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san! Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san, are you still angry?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect? \NSeeing how you filled the tub with bubbles! {lol? maybe the old subs were right in that other line but they totally got this one wrong somehow; at least this gives some clues as to why the other women were angry?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be clowning around!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.79,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't go there, I'll have to go\Nall the way to the next station!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.27,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be angry!\NI'll give you a nice blowjob!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm gonna study for my entrance exams now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna do it so bad, go do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.92,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then, I'll do it by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.43,0:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.84,0:07:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're applying to college next year too, aren't you? \NDon't come crying to me if your grades tank.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I already got accepted \Nthrough recommendation.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Probably bought your way in with money.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The German Peasants' War?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,1524.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Xi'an Incident in China?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,December 1936.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's basic knowledge.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She got it right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.82,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuno! When did Napoleon escape from Elba?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,1815...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Fronde rebellion?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... 1648.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Egyptian–Turkish War?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From 1831...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ah... to '33.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Congress of Vienna!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,1814 to 1815.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.00,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Every European nation \Nexcept Turkey gathered in Vienna.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.10,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To rebuild Europe's international order \Nafter the Napoleonic Wars.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san, let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what an insane car.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.89,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno? You had a driver's license?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I've been driving around the yard \Nsince elementary school.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go to my house now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.00,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't want to?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.67,0:09:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind it, of course... \Nbut maybe another time.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.42,0:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san doesn't love me at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You just played around with me \Nand now you're tossing me out like garbage!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second, Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.93,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Yuno?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.61,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What a huge fence... I had no idea \Nthere was a U.S. military base around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my house.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.04,0:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The grounds are thirty kilometers around.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The town uses it as a marathon course.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, milady.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.41,0:10:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry along.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.59,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.52,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san, this is my mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chikanaka Rokuro-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking such good care of my daughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.41,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well... I actually haven't done much for her yet. {caring ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.88,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Admirable honesty! {???????? old subs: Aren't you an impatient one.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you intend to get married?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, once we have a baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.93,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, a baby?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.35,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.29,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still only thirty-nine! \NAnd now I'm supposed to become a grandmother?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.59,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.82,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on, why are we \Njumping so far ahead already?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.12,0:12:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize that merely dating \Na daughter of the Mamiya family
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.71,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,requires passing a qualification \Nscreening first, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.78,0:12:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If Grandma were to hear about this, \Nthere'd be hell to pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.79,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Yuno, if you rush into marriage, \Nyou'll just get bored of each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.31,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! I-It was j-just an offhand comment... {lit: I didn't try to include any deep meaning into it}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.76,0:12:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me! I knew something was fishy lately... you've been cheating on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Mama! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yuno, help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.67,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always like this, \Nchasing after younger women!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?! \NOur daughter is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.49,0:12:37.15,Top,,0,0,0,,I'm mortified! I'm going to be a grandmother at 39!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,I see... Like mother, like daughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hear what?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About the guy milady brought home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I heard!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's her boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's studying for college entrance exams!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.25,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Think they've already done it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.19,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think they'll get married?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they will.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And someday he'll inherit the Mamiya Group.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky her.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should try seducing him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.06,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But even as a mistress of a Mamiya family member, I'll be set for life! {nigou (literally "number 2")}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.95,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the restroom?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.17,0:13:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really do it in a place like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.07,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.30,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some help?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't hold back.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do whatever you want with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.13,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But in return, once you marry milady, \Nplease make me your mistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... H-Hey, cut it out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning on having \Nany woman besides Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say that! I'd even be happy \Nbeing number four or five. {analogous to nigou previously}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on a second, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{??? probs meaningless?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Chikanaka-kun, hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.18,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir. About earlier, \Nthat wasn't what you think it is...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.51,0:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've gone for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.88,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.94,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, how are things in that department?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My... about how many minutes \Nuntil you pass out?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't pass out or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you still never knew \Na woman's true pleasure...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me, if I'm not brought to the point of fainting...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I beat the living daylights out of him! {??? bunnagu? hit hard?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.11,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. \NI will handle this somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Rokuro-kun, where are you applying?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir, Ansei University, Faculty of Economics.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.30,0:15:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? If you're going to marry Yuno, \Nthen you'd better study hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.03,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start drilling business management into you early.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.57,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Madam and the young lady apparently have some very important special training to attend to,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so they wished to be excused from dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.99,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come under Madam's orders. \NI am Guillotine Ranko.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.18,0:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With five years of experience in striptease industry, \NI shall train you thoroughly. {hanadensha performances - hanadensha (literally "flower train") is a type of stage entertainment in which the woman uses her vaginal muscles to perform some tricks, similar to https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ping_pong_show - flower trains were streetcars with decorations that ran on holidays and carried no passengers, so this kind of prostitution for show where you don't directly engage in sex with anyone but only provide visual entertainment also came to be called that}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.46,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let us begin at once. \NPlease remove your panties.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Panties? Um... what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the instructor here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not interrupt. \NJust do as you're told.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Try squeezing it. {tighten your vagina around my hand}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.82,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then, watch this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.34,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.96,0:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means to squeeze it properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.52,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No! What is this?! \NIt hurts, let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, that's... {your panties}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't even do this much, \Nyou can hardly call yourself a proper woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.95,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am humbled. You far surpass \Neverything I had ever thought possible. {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, until next time...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.89,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.71,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way I can do something like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything depends on training.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, lay down.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.70,0:16:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.63,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do to me this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My, aren't we sensitive.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.71,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! This isn't the time for lesbian games!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No no no no!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.51,0:17:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good. Remember this feeling.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going until you can \Nconsciously squeeze it that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.13,0:17:29.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I go through all this and it ends up being useless, \NI'm gonna resent Mom for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.54,0:17:41.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,I wound up in one hell of a place.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,Wonder what Yuno's up to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,She just dumped me here all by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.88,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drop it. \NWe'll gradually make it heavier from here on.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.24,0:18:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno, how's it going?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My! What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna do this anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already perfectly satisfied as things are now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the most important thing is love.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beep. Wrong answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.62,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only dated him a little, and already \Nyou're saying things like that? Oh, that's hilarious.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.55,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{cartoonish laughter sfx ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.65,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me laugh. “Love,” she says. \NOh, honestly, that's too funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why do you have to put it like that?! {manner of speaking}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno, feeling pleasure is everything for a woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are things you keep tied down with your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.95,0:18:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep saying naive things like that, \Nhe'll cheat on you and you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about you, Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.06,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mom, w-wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.79,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm enjoying myself just fine as it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You do your best too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.82,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you truly were strong... and all that! {parody of https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%88%B6%E3%82%88%E3%81%82%E3%81%AA%E3%81%9F%E3%81%AF%E5%BC%B7%E3%81%8B%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F - a 1938 war song "father, you were so strong" }
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sleeping so soundly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a splendid young man.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Yuno? \NSome nymphomaniac you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.99,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good boy and give yourself up! {???? otonashi?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! Don't move! Don't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy spotted to the left front!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.04,0:20:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it, move it! What happened...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I'm away, \Nyou go and assault my mother! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.83,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?! This is my bedroom! \NI'm the one who got attacked!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno, don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean “misunderstand”?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.06,0:20:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought perhaps the reason you weren't fainting \Nwas because the problem lay with Rokuro-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.90,0:20:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to investigate.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.99,0:20:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.78,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Th­-}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.82,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There doesn't seem to be anything wrong, \Nso go at it with all your might.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, goodnight.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there gaping! \NMove already!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.06,0:21:09.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is seriously suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come crying if all that stuff \Nmesses you up in the head.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your whole family kind of crazy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.75,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,About you, Rokuro-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.70,0:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We kinda just drifted into this relationship, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.51,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if someday something happens that traps the two of us, and our hearts become impossible to control? {lit: something that doesn't allow us to move freely}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to faint!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.75,0:22:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.50,0:22:40.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Because if that happened, then inside that pure white emptiness{lit: pure white insides of my head}, I might finally see something real and certain... {idk what she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.14,0:22:42.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,that's what I feel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.16,0:22:59.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanna forget everything \Nand collapse into your arms, Rokuro-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Be well and have healthy sex! {???? something's not right with the tense, it's like she's saying "we're well and having sex"}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.46,0:24:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.59,0:24:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.60,0:24:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.53,0:24:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.82,0:25:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mom! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.01,0:25:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.99,0:25:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.65,0:25:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:12.14,0:25:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackson's Concorde just landed.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.13,0:25:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Grandmother is here? {her own grandma it seems, yuno's great-grandma, if wiki is to be believed}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Find them! {lit: find and bring out}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.17,0:25:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:28.05,0:25:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... W-Well, if it isn't mother! \NWhat brings you all the way back from America?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.39,0:25:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother! It has been far too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.01,0:25:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arrival was so sudden, \Nplease forgive my appearance.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.14,0:25:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Had we known, we would have \Nprepared a proper welcome, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.07,0:25:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigezo, since when did you \Nbecome such a spineless fool? {her son I think?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.15,0:25:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Um... whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:48.16,0:25:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! What were you thinking, \Nallowing some nobody brat into the Mamiya family?!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.95,0:25:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.10,0:25:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that nobody she's talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:59.37,0:26:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! \NLet go of me, dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.78,0:26:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.19,0:26:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts! Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:03.58,0:26:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey, what do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.88,0:26:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:07.11,0:26:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go already! \NCan't you people listen?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:10.09,0:26:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to her. Throw him out! \NI can't stand the sight of him.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:13.45,0:26:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:14.81,0:26:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno, forget about that boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.47,0:26:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall find you a suitable husband myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:19.16,0:26:21.06,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:25.02,0:26:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:27.07,0:26:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:32.05,0:26:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, please! \NWhat are you going to do to Rokuro-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:35.13,0:26:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, please, I'm begging you, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.54,0:26:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No... wait... what are you... Ah, Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:40.71,0:26:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.37,0:26:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! If you don't like him, \Nyou can just talk it over with Rokuro-san! {?????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.19,0:26:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't take him away!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.30,0:26:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.85,0:26:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:59.39,0:27:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:06.94,0:27:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.88,0:27:35.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,D-Do you need a maiden? {03:03}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:36.30,0:27:37.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.52,0:27:42.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,Because, you know... I want to faint! {22:22}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:45.52,0:27:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. {??? maybe "I'm an idiot"}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:47.48,0:27:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,G'night! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:47.48,0:27:50.13,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on... leaving already?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:50.13,0:27:51.45,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ah, you want an umbrella?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:51.45,0:27:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:56.30,0:28:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there! You bump into somebody \Nand can't even apologize?!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.41,0:28:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No damn manners! {????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.16,0:28:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Everyone in the world treats me like dirt!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.05,0:28:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if you're rich?! Bastards!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.30,0:28:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show them... {yatteru - to that yakuza it sounds like "I'll fuck you up"}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:18.80,0:28:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.26,0:28:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show all of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.30,0:28:29.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:29.98,0:28:30.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:31.19,0:28:31.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.65,0:28:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:03.81,0:29:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency! \NIntrusion alarm confirmed in Southeast E-7 Block!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:06.96,0:29:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Put the image up on the main screen.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:09.57,0:29:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:14.30,0:29:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.67,0:29:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Madam, a man believed to be Chikanaka Rokuro has infiltrated the grounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:20.36,0:29:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:21.30,0:29:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That insolent brat... \Nthrow him out immediately!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.30,0:29:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If he resists, you may dispose of him. {kill}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:27.22,0:29:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.42,0:30:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Where are you going, milady? Please wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:22.64,0:30:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Great-Grandmother!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:24.18,0:30:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.81,0:30:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Call off the attack right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:27.64,0:30:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.06,0:30:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy will ruin the Mamiya family.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.30,0:30:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that? \NWhy are you so sure?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:33.77,0:30:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:35.42,0:30:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys like that only come sniffing around \Nfor money or status.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.15,0:30:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! \NRokuro-san isn't like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.74,0:30:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And how exactly would you know such a thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.45,0:30:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:50.04,0:30:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! No answer! {can't say anything}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.86,0:30:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just trust him.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:53.50,0:30:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget him! \NWhat good is that going to do? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:55.79,0:30:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I trust him!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:57.96,0:31:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Then let's see just how strong that trust is.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:08.81,0:31:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You old hag!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.64,0:31:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! \NHey, Yuno, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:18.15,0:31:20.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,I was young once too, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.83,0:31:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinzaburo-san, I brought the rice.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:30.66,0:31:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinzaburo-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.46,0:31:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.68,0:31:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinzaburo-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:50.98,0:31:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, you've gotten thin. \NWon't you come back home already?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:55.27,0:31:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:57.01,0:31:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:58.82,0:32:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to Shinzaburo-san?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:01.01,0:32:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I did nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:02.09,0:32:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:03.42,0:32:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely gave him money.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.06,0:32:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:10.08,0:32:13.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Chiyo... I was too naive.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:13.66,0:32:18.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,With my own strength, \NI can't even provide you a decent meal.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:19.13,0:32:21.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make you suffer any longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:21.98,0:32:23.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just forget about me!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:31.89,0:32:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:33.87,0:32:35.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,So that's why it was so easy to get in...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:13.22,0:33:16.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san, wait for me! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:35.83,0:33:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.54,0:33:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:40.90,0:33:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.88,0:33:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:28.09,0:34:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:34.76,0:34:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.97,0:34:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san! Let's do it! Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.95,0:34:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it now!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:43.48,0:34:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:10.42,0:35:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting position... {???? taii}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:16.68,0:35:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow! Huh? I can't pull it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:19.61,0:35:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! What is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:21.89,0:35:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:24.56,0:35:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:24.56,0:35:26.11,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ugh! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:26.11,0:35:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See? This is because you went \Nand did all that weird training!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:28.71,0:35:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:29.54,0:35:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've gotta somehow \Nescape this place first!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.37,0:35:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, what's the situation inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:36.11,0:35:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,FUBAR. {Complete chaos, I think? not sure how "twisted" fits into this}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.04,0:35:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.81,0:35:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming out!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:41.41,0:35:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno, ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:43.75,0:35:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Together to the very end!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.68,0:35:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready... go!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:54.63,0:35:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That truly was the ultimate retreat.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:00.33,0:36:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd they end up like that? No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:02.81,0:36:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out! This isn't a sideshow!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:05.26,0:36:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:08.51,0:36:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disaster, seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:11.63,0:36:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll have to cut it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:13.50,0:36:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:14.25,0:36:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:15.32,0:36:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. A muscle relaxant \Ninjection should loosen it.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:18.42,0:36:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:25.83,0:36:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:28.67,0:36:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-Idiot! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:32.26,0:36:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:33.95,0:36:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:35.59,0:36:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:36.86,0:36:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san, you really left your pants behind!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:40.33,0:36:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not much better yourself. {lit: similar thing}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:46.85,0:36:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go home?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:49.02,0:36:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:53.48,0:36:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{yo what is that guy from karate-bu doing there}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:06.83,0:37:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Madam's audience! {this whole scene is a parody of https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T%C5%8Dyama_no_Kin-san }
Dialogue: 10,0:37:16.88,0:37:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you old hag, what's your deal?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:19.24,0:37:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Quit screwing around already!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:22.13,0:37:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:37:24.10,0:37:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, I've had enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:27.71,0:37:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop tormenting them any further!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.33,0:37:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Pulling all this elaborate crap... {referring to her organizing this masqueraded trial}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.83,0:37:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody call Magistrate Kin-san! {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T%C5%8Dyama_no_Kin-san}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:35.92,0:37:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:37.54,0:37:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you ingrates have to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:39.82,0:37:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:37:41.94,0:37:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I've gained a bit of respect for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:45.39,0:37:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear now that you truly care \Nfor Yuno enough to risk your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.96,0:37:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that alone isn't enough \Nto survive in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.78,0:37:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to continue seeing Yuno, then prepare a dowry of 200 million yen immediately as proof of your worth.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.04,0:38:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then you'll approve of us?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:00.72,0:38:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,200... million?!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:03.26,0:38:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, Rokuro-san \Nis still just a cram school student!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:06.89,0:38:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you babbling?! \NA man who may someday join the Mamiya family
Dialogue: 10,0:38:11.54,0:38:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,should at least be capable of that much!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:14.12,0:38:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful, Rokuro-san? \NShe says just 200 million is enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:17.78,0:38:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“Just”?! {/only}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:19.34,0:38:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Rokuro-san? \NAren't you happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:22.36,0:38:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can finally be together.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:26.04,0:38:28.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,We live in completely different worlds...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.29,0:38:32.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,So this is where it ends...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:35.25,0:38:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, the matter is settled.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:38.97,0:38:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no! Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:41.08,0:38:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rokuro-san, what's wrong?! \NSay something, Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:45.27,0:38:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san! Rokuro-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:50.44,0:38:52.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,The storm-like days passed by. {this following sequence feels like a reference to some other work but eh, idc}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:53.02,0:38:57.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even now, I still don't understand \Nwhat that strength I had back then really was.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:58.15,0:39:02.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,After Yuno disappeared, I went back to being just another student preparing for exams,
Dialogue: 10,0:39:02.36,0:39:07.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,and now that my life is perfectly ordinary again, \NI've started to think I've become a pretty boring guy. {lit: now that I don't do theater ... - think he means "now that together with yuno all this over-the-top excitement is gone from my life"}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:07.03,0:39:11.10,Top,,0,0,0,,Now then, today is a very meaningful day.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:11.10,0:39:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, man...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:12.72,0:39:15.46,Top,,0,0,0,,{????}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:13.25,0:39:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No good... dammit! {?? dameda?}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:16.34,0:39:22.64,Top,,0,0,0,,The people who truly bring light into our lives \Noften disappear way too soon. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:20.07,0:39:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:22.64,0:39:25.57,Top,,0,0,0,,Of course, our scientific knowledge has expanded greatly. {??????? }
Dialogue: 10,0:39:25.57,0:39:29.98,Top,,0,0,0,,And yet, we still have little understanding \Nwhat draws people to each other. {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:29.98,0:39:33.77,Top,,0,0,0,,Perhaps what each one of us needs \Nis someone to open the door for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.67,0:40:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:01.42,0:40:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ran away from home!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:10.52,0:40:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everything I have.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:31.91,0:40:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Target confirmed. \NPrepare for airdrop.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:36.96,0:40:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes... it's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:45.59,0:40:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Airdrop!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:59.73,0:41:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:01.16,0:41:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:02.92,0:41:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:04.25,0:41:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno? Yuno! Yuno! Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:09.53,0:41:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:13.12,0:41:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:17.08,0:41:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:18.94,0:41:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You nearly wet yourself \Nover the thought of 200 million yen, {?????? very unsure but I think she says "was scared to death and peed yourself"}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:22.40,0:41:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you dare lay hands on my Yuno again?! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:26.42,0:41:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you old hag! \NI'm never letting Yuno go again!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:30.93,0:41:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His fighting spirit has returned.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:32.91,0:41:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, what exactly are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:35.97,0:41:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings well enough now. \NDo as you please.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:39.48,0:41:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That money is my farewell gift to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:42.39,0:41:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are never to cross the threshold of the Mamiya family estate again, understood?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:46.32,0:41:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yuno...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:47.68,0:41:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the man who got scared of a mere 200 million yen and tried to abandon you. {???? scared of the thought of having to collect that kind of money ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:52.48,0:41:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better keep a tight hold on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:56.16,0:41:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokuro-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:57.50,0:41:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm not gonna lose again.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:03.63,0:42:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:05.32,0:42:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:07.17,0:42:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what did you feel? {w/e that means}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:12.85,0:42:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a vision of you, Rokuro-san. {??????? lit: I saw Rokuro-san. - maybe he asked "what did you see when you fainted" but how does he know she did? maybe he asks what made grandma change her mind? no fucking clue; maybe this all is actually an obscure verb for "fainted" somehow?}
